start: ^URGENT! We have report that a rabid dog was spotted near the school and has bitten a few students. Its undoubtably release by someone as some sort of last ditch effort. But don't worry, we have sent people over to take care of it now.

^But Rabies is still a very dangerous thing to deal with and if not handle ASAP then there could be even more deaths. Find and get a sample from them ASAP. We still need to see if the virus can be cured by normal means.
